3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper proposes fingerprinting methods for multiple pattern matching, which involves techniques from discrete mathematics such as hashing and encoding. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the efficiency of the proposed algorithms and compares them with previous algorithms, which is a topic of interest in computational complexity.
